<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="about-left">
    <span class="about-label">ABOUT US</span>
    <h2 class="about-title">
      We believe technology<br />should work for you,<br />not the other way around.
    </h2>
    <a href="#" class="about-link">
      <span>Learn More About IT Dog</span>
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="about-right">
    <p>
      IT Dog was founded with a simple mission: to make enterprise-grade IT
      accessible to small and medium businesses. We understand that SMEs need
      reliable, scalable solutions without the complexity and cost of traditional
      IT consulting.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our team of experienced engineers and designers work closely with each
      client to deliver tailored solutions — from beautiful, conversion-focused
      websites to robust cloud infrastructure that grows with your business.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    display: flex;
    gap: 80px;
    padding: 80px 120px;
  }

  .about-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .about-label {
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }

  .about-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-secondary);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--foreground);
    padding: 12px 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .about-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .about-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .about-right p {
    font-family: var(--font-secondary);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 40px;
      padding: 48px 24px;
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
